WEBVTT

00:08:28.667 --> 00:08:30.910
Claim your experience.

00:08:30.910 --> 00:08:32.559
Don't let it claim you.

00:08:32.559 --> 00:08:37.431
He decided that the meaning of his experience

00:08:37.431 --> 00:08:41.198
was to know the joy of friendship,

00:08:41.198 --> 00:08:45.806
and then learn to make friends.

00:08:45.806 --> 00:08:49.792
So what about you?

00:08:49.792 --> 00:08:52.145
How are you going to find meaning

00:08:52.145 --> 00:08:54.592
in your crappy experience?

00:08:54.592 --> 00:08:56.483
It could be a recent one,

00:08:56.483 --> 00:08:58.454
or it could be one that you've been carrying around

00:08:58.454 --> 00:09:02.345
for a really long time.